{
  "stem": "5799.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't have any mules, like the Israeli Army had with the English, when they fought with the mules, and with the Aussies, with the Australians.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But there-- there were quite a few Jews, young Jews, who didn't know any-- any-- were maybe not educated, whatever, but they knew they were the salt of the earth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they inherited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they, from them, there are many thousands others-- the children and the grandchildren now.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some of my friends, who got married at 17, and who were-- had married children at  38, and became grandmothers at 40, so by now, we have-- they have great grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whoever heard living that long and seeing?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a privilege.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think, if you want to ask me anything else, by all means.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The experiences-- it's a long life, and it's hard to forgive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we must learn not to forget, but not to live with hatred.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mm-mm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It destroys.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We must learn to be aware and build-- build in our children and our grandchildren the strength, because it can happen any place, at anytime, to anybody.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's enough to look in Europe what's going on now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I really don't know what to think, because Tito was my hero.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He sent to us messages, arm and fight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Croats and the rest fought with the Nazis, so I am completely at loss there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember, when I used to be angry at somebody, I used to say, I'll Balkanize you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So we didn't have much hope for the Balkans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the Serbs were our friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They helped us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Tito helped us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Tito said, if I'm going to build communism, Stalin, you don't interfere, and America, you don't interfere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm building my own.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I know what my people need.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
